The '''Starlight Entertainers''' were a troupe of performers who were popular in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] at the beginning of the [[Jedi Civil War]]. Their manager, [[Bib Surool]], was on [[Taris/Legends|Taris]] at the time of its [[Destruction of Taris|bombardment]] by [[Darth Malak]].

